title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Falness/Charch/Russo/Burns/Robson
description: Eric Nordquist fills in for Paul Allen today! The Wild Radio Network's Kevin Falness swings by to talk hockey, Paul Charchian shares his thoughts on the Vikings and fantasy playoffs, The Athletic's Michael Russo talks NHL expansion, Ryan Burns from Gopher Illustrated previews the Quick Lane Bowl, and Britt Robson from The Athletic recaps an exciting, come-from-behind Timberwolves victory!
